This is feasible and strong enough to become a central architectural feature:

> **The agent does not repeatedly rediscover the electrical network. It operates against a persistent, versioned model graph and asks PowerFactory only for fresh state or simulation truth.**

For Build Week, do not attempt a full Graphify-equivalent.

Build one polished version:

```text
PowerFactory project
→ one-click graph index
→ interactive topology graph
→ scoped agent context queries
→ load-flow result overlay
→ context invalidated/refreshed after changes
```

That would be both technically credible and very visible in a demo.
